      "message": "[🟡 Suggestions] Line 248: `bubbleTextBody` is cached without including style-dependent inputs. `styling.textFont` and `linkColor` are embedded into the attributed result, but `invalidateTextPresentationCache()` is not called from `updateTextColor()` / `updateTextFont()`. Theme, incoming/outgoing state, or dynamic type changes can therefore leave stale link colors/fonts in already-rendered rich text. Invalidate the bubble cache whenever styling inputs change, or cache only the markdown/plain parsing and apply style at render time.",
